            Yes, it does!
            Answered by: crashnash
Date published: 2017-06-27




            I am very satisfied with this product applied on my kitchen cabinet. Is it safe to apply it and i...
        

            I am very satisfied with this product applied on my kitchen cabinet. Is it safe to apply it and its sister product Howard Feed and Wax on dinner table since they'll come in contact with food?
        
Asked by: treepruner

            The restorer would work on your table, as for the sister product. I am not sure. Not having ever done a dining table before I can't honestly help you there, I apologize for that.
            Answered by: Darkstar
Date published: 2017-07-16




            can you use this on wood floor for a spot repair
        

